Class Device.Errors

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.enhancell.remote.Device.Errors
  • Enclosing interface:
    Device

    public static final class Device.Errors
extends java.lang.Object
    Errors class contains defines for device errors. To check for a particular error a bitwise AND operation should be performed.
